flowchart TD
    Start([NFA Sent for Approval<br/>Status: ACTIVE]) --> InitApprovers[Approvers Added as Members<br/>All can VIEW<br/>Only Current can Approve]
    
    InitApprovers --> Approver1{Approver 1<br/>Reviews NFA}
    
    Approver1 -->|Needs Info| AddClarifier1[Can Add Clarifier]
    AddClarifier1 -.-> ClarificationFlow1[See Clarification Flow]
    ClarificationFlow1 -.-> Approver1
    
    Approver1 -->|Needs More Approvers| AddApprover1[Can Add New Approver<br/>to Sequence]
    AddApprover1 --> UpdateOrder1[(Update Approver List<br/>Tracked edit history)]
    UpdateOrder1 --> Approver1
    
    Approver1 -->|Approve| RecordApproval1[(Record Approval<br/>Timestamp)]
    Approver1 -->|Reject| RecordRejection1[Record Rejection<br/>Status: REJECTED]
    RecordRejection1 --> End1([Process Ends])
    
    RecordApproval1 --> NotifyNext2[Notify Approver 2]
    NotifyNext2 --> Approver2{Approver 2<br/>Reviews NFA}
    
    Approver2 -->|Needs Info| AddClarifier2[Can Add Clarifier]
    AddClarifier2 -.-> ClarificationFlow2[See Clarification Flow]
    ClarificationFlow2 -.-> Approver2
    
    Approver2 -->|Needs More Approvers| AddApprover2[Can Add New Approver<br/>to Sequence]
    AddApprover2 --> UpdateOrder2[(Update Approver List<br/>Tracked edit history)]
    UpdateOrder2 --> Approver2
    
    Approver2 -->|Approve| RecordApproval2[(Record Approval<br/>Timestamp)]
    Approver2 -->|Reject| RecordRejection2[Record Rejection<br/>Status: REJECTED]
    RecordRejection2 --> End2([Process Ends])
    
    RecordApproval2 --> CheckMore{More<br/>Approvers?}
    
    CheckMore -->|Yes| NotifyNext[Notify Next Approver<br/>Order n+1]
    NotifyNext --> ApproverN{Approver N<br/>Reviews NFA}
    
    ApproverN -->|Approve| RecordApprovalN[(Record Approval)]
    ApproverN -->|Reject| RecordRejectionN[Status: REJECTED]
    RecordRejectionN --> EndN([Process Ends])
    ApproverN -->|Add Clarifier| ClarificationFlowN[Clarification Process]
    ClarificationFlowN -.-> ApproverN
    ApproverN -->|Add Approver| UpdateOrderN[(Update Sequence)]
    UpdateOrderN --> ApproverN
    
    RecordApprovalN --> CheckMore
    
    CheckMore -->|No| FinalApproval[All Approvers Completed<br/>Status: APPROVED]
    FinalApproval --> Archive[Archive NFA<br/>No Further Edits Allowed]
    Archive --> EndSuccess([NFA Approved])
    
    note1[Note: Approvers can see NFA<br/>once added to members<br/>but can only approve when<br/>their turn arrives]
    note2[Note: During approval process<br/>edits to NFA details are<br/>tracked as history]
    
    style RecordApproval1 fill:#90EE90
    style RecordApproval2 fill:#90EE90
    style RecordApprovalN fill:#90EE90
    style FinalApproval fill:#90EE90
    style RecordRejection1 fill:#FFB6C6
    style RecordRejection2 fill:#FFB6C6
    style RecordRejectionN fill:#FFB6C6
    style UpdateOrder1 fill:#E6E6FA
    style UpdateOrder2 fill:#E6E6FA
    style UpdateOrderN fill:#E6E6FA

